title: What Celebrities Make Bobby’s Wedding Guest List? + Amy Saves A Life…Sorta! + Bobby’s Mailbag: Naming Your Daughter ‘Karen’
itunes:title: What Celebrities Make Bobby’s Wedding Guest List? + Amy Saves A Life…Sorta! + Bobby’s Mailbag: Naming Your Daughter ‘Karen’
description:
Bobby talks about beginning the wedding guest list process. He said he’d like to have a performance area for his artist friends to perform (with no pressure of course!) We wonder who will make the guest list. Amy talks about a scary situation at her house that ended up saving a man’s life! Bobby reads an email from a listener who is debating with their wife about naming their daughter ‘Karen’.
